  "texts": [
    "In accordance with the outcomes of our experiments, we set the hyperparameters as follows:• For GRMF, we set d = p = 0.1 and l = 0.2.• In DTINet, the restart probability for random walk was set to r = 0.8, and k 1 = 100 and k 1 = 400 were used.",
    "• NGDTP was configured with f r = 280 and f r = 210 in the matrix decomposition step, and a 1 = a 2 = a 3 = 0.1.",
    "I • In the GBDT model, we set num leaves = 80 and a learning rate of 0.02.• For MolTrans, we used a Batch Size of 16, Learning Rate of 0.0001, Epoch of 30, and Dropout of 0.1.",
    "() TPR = TP TP + FN, (15) FPR = FP FP + TN,16= TP TP + FP,(17) Precision= TP TP + FN.",
    "((18) Recall) MCC = TP × TN -FP × FN √ (TP + FP)(TP + FN)(TN + FP)(TN + FN).19TTGCN was trained and optimized using PyTorch on a GPU device (Nvidia GeForce GTX 3070)."
